column12: Activists say that public order officers pushed Elly into the nearby river and then threw stones at her until she drowned.
Sally died as a result of a bashed in skull.

Kellie was strangled to death with a scarf by 18 year old Shanniel Hyatt.

He then covered her body with a white blanket - with the brown furry scarf used to choke her still bound tightly round her neck. Hyatt said he killer her after discovering she had a penis.
